goal of asg is to:
scale out ec2 to match increase load
scale in to mathc decreased load
ensure we have max and no of machines running 
automatically register insatnces to load balancer

asg has following attributes:
ami+instance type
ec2 user data
ec2 insatnces
keypairs
ebs vlols
min/max size
nw and subnets info
load balancer info
scaling policy

possibleto scale asg based on cloudbwatch alarms based on any metric

asg literally terminates instances and creates new one
